gth-entries have default values containing\nenough digits, e.g. /Length 000 when the stream consists of 576 bytes.\n\nExample:\n   update-offsets --verbose --encoding ISO-8859-1 issue-297.pdf issue-297.out.pdf"], "functions": [{"name": "pdfly.update_offsets.update_lines", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "lines_in", "type": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "encoding", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "console", "type": {"name": "Console", "xref": {"fqname": "rich.console.Console", "project": "rich"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "verbose", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Iterates over the lines of a pdf-files and updates offsets.\n\nThe input is expected to be a pdf without binary-sections.\n\n```\nparam lines_in\n\nA list over the lines including line-breaks.\n\nparam encoding\n\nThe encoding, e.g. \"iso-8859-1\" or \"UTF-8\".\n\nparam console\n\nConsole used to print messages.\n\nparam verbose\n\nTrue to activate logging of info-messages.\n```\n\n:return The output is a list of lines to be written\n\n: in the given encoding.\n"]}, {"name": "pdfly.update_offsets.read_binary_file", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "file_path", "type": {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "encoding", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Reads a binary file line by line and returns these lines as a list of strings in the given encoding.\nEncoding utf-8 can't be used to read random binary data.\n\n```\nparam file_path\n\nfile to be read line by line\n\nparam encoding\n\nencoding to be used (e.g. \"iso-8859-1\")\n```\n\n\\:return lines including line-breaks\n"]}, {"name": "pdfly.update_offsets.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "file_in", "type": {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "file_out", "type": {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "encoding", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "verbose", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "pdfly.update_offsets.List", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pdfly.update_offsets.RE_OBJ", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pdfly.update_offsets.RE_CONTENT", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pdfly.update_offsets.RE_LENGTH_REF", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pdfly.update_offsets.RE_LENGTH", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": []}]}